       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CALCULATE-PENALTY.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-PENALTY-RATE        PIC V999 VALUE 0.05.
       01 WS-MINIMUM-PENALTY     PIC S9(5)V99 VALUE 10.00.
       01 WS-CALCULATED-PENALTY  PIC S9(7)V99 COMP-3.

       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01 LS-ACCOUNT-BALANCE     PIC S9(9)V99 COMP-3.
       01 LS-PENALTY-AMOUNT      PIC S9(7)V99 COMP-3.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING LS-ACCOUNT-BALANCE
                                LS-PENALTY-AMOUNT.
       CALCULATE-PENALTY-MAIN.
           IF LS-ACCOUNT-BALANCE >= 0
               MOVE ZERO TO LS-PENALTY-AMOUNT
           ELSE
               COMPUTE WS-CALCULATED-PENALTY =
                   ABS(LS-ACCOUNT-BALANCE) * WS-PENALTY-RATE

               IF WS-CALCULATED-PENALTY < WS-MINIMUM-PENALTY
                   MOVE WS-MINIMUM-PENALTY TO LS-PENALTY-AMOUNT
               ELSE
                   MOVE WS-CALCULATED-PENALTY TO LS-PENALTY-AMOUNT
               END-IF
           END-IF

           EXIT PROGRAM.

       VALIDATE-PENALTY-CALCULATION.
           IF LS-PENALTY-AMOUNT < 0
               MOVE ZERO TO LS-PENALTY-AMOUNT
           END-IF.
